    "description": "University is an influential and strategic time in a young person's life. Through our presence on campus, we desire to see students become lifelong followers of Christ and missional influencers among their peers and in their communities. Our personnel needs include lecturers in various fields, who will live out their Christian faith on campus; campus \"pastors\" who will disciple students and organise campus ministries; and short-term interns looking for experience in campus ministry."
