    "description": "TEAM has medical opportunities in various areas of the world that may be the perfect fit. From bustling hospitals in the Middle East to public healthcare opportunities in rural African villages, our global workers use their medical backgrounds in a variety of ways to share the love of Christ and build up the local church."
